name: Hangukgwan
description: Hangukgwan is the name of the restaurant on the second floor across the street in this image. I often name my pieces based on an item in the photography, and in this case, the restaurant's light radiates across the entire image.  It is also the case that this restaurant in particular is open for 24 hours, which makes it even more appealing to me since I was out taking pictures in the rain up until morning. Despite being so late at night, there were still plenty of people out exploring the city, which is one reason why I like this image. The hustle and bustle of Seoul, South Korea past midnight.
